# Immovable Cultural Heritage in the Kosovo District

This list includes Immovable Cultural Heritage sites (listed by the ) which are located in the Kosovska Mitrovica District of Serbia – which, except for not including the municipality of Novo Brdo, overlaps with the District of Pristina and District of Ferizaj of Kosovo.
